            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Hd1e108">Rubrica 5</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De meditatione mortis et vite</head>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-d1e114">
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>¶ De meditatione mortis et vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>te. Rubrica. 5.
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-d1e121">
      <!--327.xml-->
          <pb ed="#V" n="144-v"/>
          <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
        <lb ed="#V" n="1"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Rd1e124">IEsus filius sirach: in ecclesiastico.
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>capitulo 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Qd1e134">In omnibus operibus
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>tuis memorare nouissima tua: et in
        <lb ed="#V" n="4" break="no"/>eternum non peccabis.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-d1e142"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Rd1e140">4. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Qd1e144">Memor
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>esto: quia mors non tardat.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-d1e151"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Rd1e151">28. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Qd1e153">Memento
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>nouissimorum: et desine inimicari: tabitudo enim
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>et mors imminet in mandatis.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-d1e161"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh0451-Rd1e163">41. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Qd1e163">O mors
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>quam amara est memoria tua homini iniusto et pa
        <lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>cem habenti in substantiis suis: viro quieto: et cu
        <lb ed="#V" n="10" break="no"/>ius vie directe sunt in omnibus et adhuc va
        <lb ed="#V" n="11" break="no"/>lenti accipere cibum.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-d1e175">
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Rd1e181">Tullius de senectute:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Qd1e179">Nemo est tam senex qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>se annum non putet posse viuere.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-d1e185">
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Rd1e193">Persius satyra. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Qd1e189">Uiue memor leti: fugit
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>hora.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-d1e195">
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Rd1e205">Quintilianus declamationum. 3. declamatione.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Qd1e199">In
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>turpissima perpetuitatis <sic>cagitatione</sic> destricti per
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>exigua festinantis eui momenta praemorimur.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-d1e207">
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Rd1e219">Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum. libro i. capitulo 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Qd1e211">Nulli potes
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>secura vita contingere qui producenda nimis co
        <lb ed="#V" n="21" break="no"/>gitat.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-d1e220"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Rd1e232">libro 19. epistola 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Qd1e222">Nihil eque tibi profuerit ad
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>temperantiam omnium rerum quam frequens cogitatio bre
        <lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>uis eui: et huius incerti: quicquid facies respice
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>ad mortem.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-d1e232"> 
      / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Rd1e246">Idem de consolatione ad marciam</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Qd1e234">In hoc omnes errore versamur vt non putemus
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>ad mortem nisi senes inclinatosque iam vergere.</quote>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-d1e242">
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Rd1e260">Hieronymus in prologo principii biblie
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>ad finali.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e10451-Qd1e246">Facile contemnit omnia qui se semper
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>cogitat moriturum.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
